    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <head type="title"><app>
                    <lem wit="#KK #B #M">Index XXII.</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P">Index XIII.</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R">Index XXI.</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2">Index XXII., in quo regnum Alberti primi imperatoris Romanorum describitur</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#S1 #S2 #S3">Index XXI. de Alberto Austriaco Romanorum imperatore, Hungariae Bohemiaeque rege</rdg>
                    </app></head>
                <p>
                <s n="1">﻿<app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P">Genuerat</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Tenuerat</rdg>
                    </app> Sigismundus ex uxore nomine Barbara Ermandi Ciliae comitis filia <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P">Elisabectam</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Elisabettam</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#Z">Elizabetam</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#L1 #L2 #M">Elizabetham</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#R #S1 #S2 #S3">Elisabetham</rdg>
                    </app>, quam vivens Alberto Austriae duci matrimonio iunxerat, illo itaque <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3">extincto</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#M">exstincto</rdg>
                    </app> Albertus et Hungarorum rex coronatur et in <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Bohemiae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Bohemie</rdg>
                        <rdg wit="#Z">Bohemia</rdg>
                    </app> regnum illi succedit, consensu <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">praeterea</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">preterea</rdg>
                    </app> eorum, quibus huiuscemodi res <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">curae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">cure</rdg>
                    </app> esse consuevit, imperator eligitur Romanorum.<note type="critic"
                        corresp="RKK">1 = Th 4.25. – <hi rend="italic">et in Bohemiae...
                            Romanorum</hi> = Th 4.26.</note></s>
                <s n="2">Fuit is magno animo vir et <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Christianae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Christiane</rdg>
                    </app> fidei defensor acerrimus.</s>
                <s n="3">Movit <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">nanque</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">namque</rdg>
                    </app> bellum adversus Hussitas, id est contra Bohemos illos, qui Ioannis
                    cognomento <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B">Hus</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Huss</rdg>
                    </app> errores contra <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">sacrosanctae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P">sacrosanctae<del><add type="insert">p</add></del><note type="critic">addit et del. litteram
                            p</note></rdg>
                    </app> catholicae <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">ecclesiae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">ecclesie</rdg>
                    </app> fidem affirmant pertinaciterque tenent ac praedicant, de quorum damnata <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">haeresi</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P">heresi</rdg>
                    </app> suo in loco, <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">quae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">que</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #B #L1 #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">fuerunt</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#Z #R">fuerint</rdg>
                    </app> cognitu necessaria, perstrinximus.</s>
                <s n="4">Duxit quidem Christianissimus princeps in illos numerosum exercitum, sed
                    occurrentibus quibusdam suarum rerum difficultatibus necesse ei fuit a suscepta
                    expeditione desistere.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">3–4 = Th 4.26. – <hi
                            rend="italic">de quorum... perstrinximus</hi> cf. Annales vol. VIII.
                        foll. 167r–177v: „Origo et progressus heresis Bohemorum.“</note></s>
                <s n="5">Parantem postea bellum adversus illos denuo gerere immatura mors rapuit,
                    quippe qui paulo minus duobus annis regnum tenuit.</s>
                <s n="6">Vita <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #B #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">excessit</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#P">excaessit</rdg>
                    </app> anno salutis <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">humanae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">humane</rdg>
                    </app>
                    <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #L2">MCCCCXXXVIIII</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B #Z #L1 #R #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">MCCCCXXXIX</rdg>
                    </app>., <app>
                        <lem wit="#KK #P #Z #L1 #R #L2 #S1 #S2 #S3 #M">Albae</lem>
                        <rdg wit="#B">Albe</rdg>
                    </app> sepultus est.<note type="critic" corresp="RKK">5–6 = Th 4.27.</note></s>
            </p>
            </div>
